    <string name="onboarding_a11y_single_title">Enable Accessibility</string>
    <string name="onboarding_a11y_single_body"><b>PlayTranslate</b> needs the Accessibility permission to work on single-screen devices.\n\nWith it, <b>PlayTranslate</b> can:\n• Capture the game screen without leaving your app\n• Show translated text as an overlay over your game\n• Look up words by dragging over game text\n• Display game screen controls\n\nIt does not read UI content, monitor input, or access personal data.</string>

